 \mathrm{Corr}(X^2,Y^2)=\frac{\mathbb E(X^2Y^2)-\mathbb E(X^2)\mathbb E(Y^2)}{\sqrt{\mathrm{var}(X^2)\mathrm{var}(Y^2)}}=\frac{1+2\varrho^2-1}{\sqrt{2\cdot2}}=\varrho^2. 
