\mathrm{Var}[X] = a^{2}+b^{2}
\mathrm{Var}[Y] = c^{2}+d^{2}
\rho_{X,Y} = \frac{ac+bd}{\sqrt{a^{2}+b^{2}}\sqrt{c^{2}+d^{2}}}
