\mathrm{Cov}(X^{2},Y^{2}) = \mathrm{Cov}(a^{2}M^{2}+b^{2}N^{2}+2abMN,c^{2}M^{2}+d^{2}N^{2}+2cdMN) =
= a^{2}c^{2}\mathrm{Var}[M^{2}] + (2a^{2}cd+2b^{2}cd+2abc^{2}+2abd^{2}) \mathrm{Cov}(M^{2},MN) +b^{2}d^{2}\mathrm{Var}[N^{2}] + 4abcd\mathrm{Cov}(MN,MN)
